          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Cybersecurity Grants for Schools Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill allows the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency to award grants or other financial assistance for cybersecurity and infrastructure security education and training programs at the elementary and secondary education levels. Entities eligible for the assistance include states, localities, institutions of higher education, and nonprofits. </p>]]>
